Hi,

I'm a newbie trying to run my unit tests and generate
test reports
from ant. All my testcases seem to run just fine and
pass, but for
some reason, they end up as 'unknown' in the JUnit
reports! For
instance, the XML contains data like this:

<testcase
classname="junit.framework.JUnit4TestCaseFacade"
name="unknown" time="0.031" />

Any thoughts as to what I'm doing wrong?

I'm using (trying to use) JUnit 4.1 and ant 1.6.5 on a
Windows box.

Thanks,
Einar
